<p style="margin: 0 0 20px;">Dear {{executorName}},</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px;">You are receiving this message because <strong>{{accountHolderName}}</strong> has designated you as an executor for their Dhanam financial account.</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff3e0; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #f57c00;">
  <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #e65100;">Extended Inactivity Detected</p>
  <p style="margin: 10px 0 0;">{{accountHolderName}} has been inactive on Dhanam for <strong>{{daysInactive}} days</strong>, which exceeds their configured Life Beat threshold.</p>
</div>

<div style="margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 15px; font-weight: 600;">What does this mean?</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;">As a designated executor, you may be eligible to request read-only access to {{accountHolderName}}'s financial overview. This is designed to help trusted individuals assist in case of emergencies or incapacitation.</p>
</div>

<div style="margin: 30px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 15px; font-weight: 600;">What should you do?</p>
  <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #333;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>First, try to contact {{accountHolderName}} directly</strong> - They may simply have been busy or traveling.</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>If you cannot reach them</strong>, you may request access through the link below.</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Access requires verification</strong> - For security, multiple executor confirmation may be required.</li>
  </ol>
</div>

{{> button text="Request Access" url=accessRequestUrl buttonColor="#1976d2"}}

<div style="margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 4px;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 600;">Important Security Information</p>
  <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #666;">
    <li>Access is read-only - you cannot make changes or transfers</li>
    <li>All actions are logged and audited</li>
    <li>Access is time-limited and can be revoked by the account holder at any time</li>
    <li>The account holder will be notified if access is granted</li>
  </ul>
</div>

