  <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #d32f2f;">This email was not expected?</p>
  <p style="margin: 10px 0 0;">If you do not know {{accountHolderName}} or believe you received this in error, please disregard this message. The access request link requires additional verification.</p>
</div>

